LambdaMF
a novel collaborative filtering method incorporating lambda

compile and produce dataset:
place the MovieLens100K dataset(u.data) and Netflix dataset(training_set/) in the same directory and run:
	sh prepare.sh

run experiments:
	sh run_experiment.sh

general usage:
	./LambdaMF -train [training data] -test [testing data] -e [eta] -L2 [L2 regularization coefficient] -n [number of iterations] -a [alpha] -train_logfile [log filename(optional)] -test_logfile [log filename(optional)]

default:
